h^* ={\bf argmax}_{{h}\in\mathbb{R}^{d}} m(h),\end{equation} 
where $v\in \mathbb{R}^d, U\in \mathbb{R}^{d\times d}$ such that $\|U\|_2 \leq L$, and $M$ is a positive constant. 

