abla L(\vx_{t-1})^	op \vDelta\}$, find an upper bound for $L(\vx_{t}) - L(\vx^*)$.

Find an if and only if condition for the statement “$\vx$ is a KKT point of $\min_{
orm{\vx}\le  rac{1}{\lambda}} L(\vx)$” in terms of $
orm{\vx}$ and $\inner{-\lambda \vx}{
abla L(\vx)}$.

