    \item When $t$ is even, $\refE[ \intH{\bm t}{\bm x_{1:\ssize}}{1}^2] \leq (Ct)^{\frac{t}{2}} \cdot  d^{-\frac{t}{2}}$.
    \item For even $t \leq \dim$, $\refE[ \intH{\bm t}{\bm x_{1:\ssize}}{1}^2] \geq (t/C)^{\frac{t}{2}} \cdot d^{-\frac{t}{2}}$. 
